Notes;

Might be more fun for the user to have a "low volatility" slot machine. A low volatility slot allows small wins that occur frequently. High volatility implies large wins that happen infrequently. 

Possibility of introducing "wild" symbols that can act as substitutes for other symbols.

Perhaps our machine can adhere to a predetermined payout percentage as in real slots. 


Persona: 

A first time slot player that has found our machine through an add or by seeing someone else using a similar application. This person is not heavily into gambling but found the idea of playing a virtual slot machine entertaining and wants to try it out. 

User stories:

1. An experienced slot player who wants to play play money slots to curb his desire to play for real money. Wants features that add elements of risk and excitement. 

2. A bored young person who usually plays modern games on their phone and is interested in finding out why slot machines are popular. They are looking for features similar to what they are used to. Overstimulation and instant gratification. 



